line_1: He soon arrived, he traced the village-green,
line_2: There saw the maid, and was with pleasure seen;

line_1: Then louder Scandal walk'd the village-green;
line_2: First, whispering gossips were in parties seen

line_1: Alas! it is not on the village-green: —
line_2: Where now is perfect resignation seen?
In white were all its maidens seen,
